description: Vantex Resources Ltd. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mining properties in Canada. The company primarily explores for gold deposit. Its property include the Cléricy property located in the Cléricy Township, Canada. The company was formerly known as Vantex Oil, Gas and Minerals Ltd. and changed its name to Vantex Resources Ltd in February 2004. Vantex Resources Ltd. was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Anthony K. Jackson B.B.A, C.A., CPA, CA, CPA
